c: 41
v: 47
t: "Kwavari (Allah) chete ndiko kune ruzivo rwenguva. Hapana muchero unobuda kubva muchinyedza chawo, kana chikadzi kuzvitakura kana kubara kusara neruzivo rwavo. Uye pazuva iro (Allah) vachadaidzira kwavari (vachiti): “Varipi vamwe vangu (vamaindisanganisa navo)?” Ivo vachati: “Tinokutaurirai kuti hapana umwe wedu anopa uchapupu kwazviri (kuti vamwe venyu)!”"